Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.44,0:00:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.57,0:00:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說二葉你是一個人來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就在家門口偶然碰見了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽說日和姐姐你們在做假期作業
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.29,0:00:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想一起做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Comment: 0,0:01:51.22,0:01:55.01,EPTitle,,0,0,0,karaoke,婚禮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:01:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說 我們要從哪裡開始寫？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:01:59.97,Default,,0,1000,0,,從理科開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:01:59.97,Default,,1000,0,0,,從文科開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,文科
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,理科
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我想先幹掉比較難的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,數學才更難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你們互相教一下怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,戀你好聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼首先就由學過英文對話的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,來教你英文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.33,0:02:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,明明對片假名過敏？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因為我不擅長記憶名詞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,或者說不擅長記憶沒有意義的羅列…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我考試分數可是很高的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.51,0:02:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我向戀申請決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,從現在開始禁止說日語 只准用英語對話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 作業要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,發音好準
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please have some cookies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you like it! It's homemade cookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:03:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I prepared it for study session
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,戀用的是完全不說話的作戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是大人間的玩樂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You are dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This... This is a...
